        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="488669664">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-488669664" class="vote-count">3</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-488669664" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="488669664">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lululove_fish/">繁體桃</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2013-02-06</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">看一部佛經就像一次思想上的和諧性愛，你來我往，水乳交融，最終通過自己的領悟力到達最high的高潮。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
